DOC.brief_summary: The aim study evaluate effect dietary supplement ( Obex® ) anthropometric physiological variable Spanish woman 35 60 year overweight obese .
DOC.brief_title: Obex , Nutritional Supplement , Overweight Obese Spanish Women
DOC.detailed_description: The nutritional supplement consist natural plant extract Caralluma fimbriata , Phaseolus vulgaris , Acai Berry antiobesity agent : ornithine , carnitine fumarate , essential fatty acid certain amino acid , vitamin mineral .
